        <p>Nullam condimentum turpis eu luctus auctor. Nam viverra nisl id odio suscipit, in dictum lectus pharetra. Curabitur nec vestibulum sapien.</p>
        <br>
        <h3>Our Team</h3>
        <p>Meet our dedicated team members who are passionate about sharing their knowledge and insights with you.</p>
        <br>
        <h3>Rohan</h3>
        <p>Full Stack Developer,Technical Content Writer</p>
        <br>
        <!-- Add more team members as needed -->
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="main-content">
          <div class="about-section">
            <!-- ... (about section content) ... -->
